Package com.quorum.tessera.api

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApiResource
    Provides HTTP endpoints for accessing the OpenAPI schema
    PartyInfoResource
    Defines endpoints for requesting node discovery (partyinfo) information
    Tessera
    The main application that is submitted to the HTTP server Contains all the service classes created by the service locator
    TransactionResource
    Provides endpoints for dealing with transactions, including: - creating new transactions and distributing them - deleting transactions - fetching transactions - resending old transactions
    UpCheckResource
    Provides endpoints about the health status of this node
    VersionResource
    Provides endpoints to determine versioning information
